data.description:
Beautiful Home – Beautiful  Setting – In one of Montana’s most Historic Areas!
2328 sf 3 Bedroom/2 Bath with outbuildings on 5.36 irrigated acres, just minutes south of Hamilton, MT
This 2007 Split Level home is surrounded by mature shade trees on a level, landscaped lawn with its large rear deck, it is cool and perfect for relaxation. The home is low maintenance, with HardiBoard Lap siding, composite decking and vinyl windows. Bring your animals to this irrigated property. With 2 wells and ditch irrigation, this property has adequate water for hobby or production farming!
